'''二茂铍'''是一种金属有机化合物，化学式为Be(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，它最初在1959年被制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Inorganic Chemistry|volume=2005|issue=16|language=en|issn=1434-1948|date=2005-08|pages=3197–3206|doi=10.1002/ejic.200500329|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/ejic.200500329|title=Recent Developments in the Chemistry of Beryllocenes|accessdate=2020-09-29|author=Rafael Fernández, Ernesto Carmona}}</ref>

==制备==
二茂铍可由[[氯化铍|氯化铍]]和[[环戊二烯基钠|环戊二烯基钠]]在[[苯|苯]]或[[乙醚|乙醚]]中反应制得：<ref name=syn>{{cite journal|journal=Chemische Berichte|volume=92|issue=2|language=de|date=1959-02|pages=482–486|doi=10.1002/cber.19590920233|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/cber.19590920233|title=Über Aromatenkomplexe von Metallen, XXV. Di-cyclopentadienyl-beryllium|accessdate=2020-09-29|author=Ernst Otto Fischer, Hermann P. Hofmann}}</ref>
:<math>\mathrm{BeCl_2 +\ 2\ Na(C_5H_5)\ \xrightarrow[]{Et_2O} Be(C_5H_5)_2 + 2\ NaCl }</math>

==性质==
二茂铍在水中剧烈反应，生成[[氢氧化铍|氢氧化铍]]和[[环戊二烯|环戊二烯]]。<ref name=syn />有文献报道它理论上可以和[[铍|铍]]发生放热反应，生成C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>BeBeC<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Xie|first1=Yaoming|last2=Schaefer|first2=Henry F.|last3=Jemmis|first3=Eluvathingal D.|title=Characteristics of novel sandwiched beryllium, magnesium, and calcium dimers: C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>BeBeC<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>, C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>MgMgC<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>, and C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CaCaC<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|volume=402|issue=4-6|year=2005|pages=414–421|issn=00092614|doi=10.1016/j.cplett.2004.11.106}}</ref>
